organizations.name: continuing operations reuters staff  cbiz inc

text:
April 26 (Reuters) - CBIZ Inc:
* CBIZ REPORTS FIRST-QUARTER 2018 RESULTS
* Q1 REVENUE ROSE 10.2 PERCENT TO $266.1 MILLION * COMPANY EXPECTS GROWTH IN TOTAL REVENUE WITHIN A RANGE OF 5% TO 8% IN 2018
* IN 2018 EXPECTS TO ACHIEVE GROWTH IN FULLY DILUTED EARNINGS PER SHARE WITHIN A RANGE OF 13% TO 17% OVER $0.92 REPORTED FOR 2017
* CBIZ - IN 2018, ADJUSTED FOR IMPACT OF TAX REFORM ACT,EXPECTS TO ACHIEVE GROWTH WITHIN RANGE OF 20% TO 24% OVER ADJUSTED $0.87 REPORTED FOR 2017 Source text for Eikon:
